	)
	(text "The reference voltage of EN and FBX are 1.6V:\n- Cutoff input voltage is 7.5V with selected resistors on EN\n- Output is adjustable from 100V to 260V with selected resistors on FBX\n\nPoti RV1 terminal 2 and 3 tied together that the poti can't fail open circuit\n→ limits VCC_HV in case of poti failure\n\n\nRT=130k compared to 107k in other designs\n→ f=330kHz, larger off-time-margin which would be near the limit at 400kHz,\n  increased ripple doesn't matter because we're just charging the power caps with the output"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.494 183.642 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "49e3b5e0-d0ee-4d8e-855f-9afe39dcb95b")
	)
	(text "Reference design:        74437324100  (10uH)\nAvailable alternative:     74438336100  (10uH, tiny)\nAvailable alternative:     74438356150  (15uH)\nBetter alternative:        74438356220  (22uH)\nPerformance alternative:  744393305220 (22uH)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 81.788 62.484 0)
		(effects
